You can't be saved in life either if it were not for the Lord's Mercy.  Does his mercy stop because we have fallen asleep?  I have experienced my brother and my dad at one Holy Pascha service being with me in the Altar.  I know they are just as part of me now as they were when they were &quot;living&quot;.  There is only a divide at our temporal understanding of time, but in the 8th day, there is no seperation.<br>
